{"tid":828693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍艦交椅洲擱淺　特區政府接通報：登陸避險","createTime":"2018-09-20T01:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T07:21:54.000Z","uid":6604,"like":227,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"5d694d3e737f8304d6d975bb7a2146cf6bf7cdb2","tid":828693,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:08:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180919/s00001/1537336822452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180919%2Fs00001%2F1537336822452&d=9HFwKgiXanrvJ1lsAHvQR2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=86fce175\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180919%2Fs00001%2F1537336822452&h=5a22efa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180919/s00001/1537336822452</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超強颱風「山竹」吹襲本港後，一艘解放軍艦在摩星嶺西邊對出的交椅洲<span style=\"color: red;\">擱淺</span>。《明報》記者今早前往視察，軍艦大部分船身剷上陸地，有3至4名解放軍身穿反光衣，於軍艦附近檢查。<br />\n<br />\n至11時許，一艘編號3358的解放軍艦駛至，向附近船隻響號及驅趕，軍艦上有20多名船員，全部身穿反光衣。其後，有9名解放軍坐上小艇前往交椅洲，岸上有4名解放軍接應，一行13人登上肇事軍艦檢查，逗留約5分鐘後返回小艇。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府其後回覆《明報》查詢時稱，在16日（星期日）「山竹」襲港期間，收到駐港部隊通報，表示有一艘駐軍軍艦<span style=\"color: red;\">登陸在交椅洲避險</span>。據了解，駐港部隊正安排撤走有關軍艦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706a8e3a93d435d8f4aa2c2488c7686ee47f5278","tid":828693,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a534cbdc4498ed08eb81692243c37ddf52a196","tid":828693,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127b31546d2f59e51badd5ee1fbe068b56ae46fa","tid":828693,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:10:43.000Z","msg":"笑4"},{"pid":"04cf40b0428f106b8252995d61d8fa1293a8451c","tid":828693,"uid":154612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72afd64c48c816ed6b8df39c8b03cd6aa480f559","tid":828693,"uid":21545,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:12:02.000Z","msg":"感謝香港政府為市民提供是日笑話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" c